high_descs: Go straight then turn left and go to the table
Pick up the fork from the table
Turn left then turn left again and go to the sink
Put the fork in the sink and fill the sink with water, then empty the water from the sink and remove the fork
Turn around, then turn left, take a step then turn left again
Put the fork in the drawer
anns.task_desc: Put the cleaned fork in a drawer

high_descs: Walk to the right side of the island on your left and when you get there turn left to face it.
Pick up the fork that's to the right of the knife.
Turn left and walk to the right side of the sink and when you get there turn left to face the area to the right of the sink.
Wash the fork in the sink and get it back out and close the tap.
Take a tiny step back and a tiny step right.
Open the drawer all the way to the right and put the fork in there and close it.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean fork in the drawer.

high_descs: Head straight and stop at the kitchen island
Grab the fork that is on the counter
Turn around and go to the sink
Wash the fork in the sink and then take it out
Back up from the counter and face the drawers
Put the fork in the top right drawer
anns.task_desc: Putting a fork in a kitchen drawer
